### Intent
Implement Phase UI chunk C1: semantic design tokens, theme/font presets, ThemeProvider, settings UI in AppLayout, and metaphor component scaffolds.

### Summary
Created `phase-ui-metaphor` branch and shipped C1 design system. Migrated all `index.css` hex values to semantic CSS custom properties; palette lives in `styles/themes/default.css`, fonts in `styles/fonts/default.css`. Added `ThemeProvider` + `useTheme()` with `localStorage` persistence and `data-theme`/`data-font` on `<html>`. AppLayout now has theme swatch + font dropdown (one preset each, extensible). Scaffolded `IndexCard`, `NotebookSpread`, and `PinnedNote` components with token-only CSS. `npm run build` passes; no hex in changed frontend files outside theme/font CSS.

### Decisions
- **Skipped Framer Motion** — optional C1 item; avoided new dependency for route transitions
- **Theme before Auth in provider tree** — appearance applies even on login/register pages
- **Inline flash-prevention script in index.html** — reads localStorage before React mount

### Changes
- `frontend/src/styles/` — `tokens.css`, `themes/default.css`, `fonts/default.css`
- `frontend/src/theme/ThemeProvider.tsx` — theme context + presets
- `frontend/src/index.css` — token imports, all colors via `var(--*)`
- `frontend/src/components/AppLayout.tsx` — appearance settings UI
- `frontend/src/components/{recipe-box,lab,corkboard}/` — scaffolds + barrel exports
- `frontend/src/main.tsx`, `frontend/index.html` — provider wiring + early theme apply

